@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_utapzt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 - tmp)
    v2 = 0.80
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.23 - v2 + 0.67)))
    v0 = wp.abs(v1)
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.sin(v1 + 0.99) - 0.57))
    v1 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.48 / v1 + 0.18)) * (0.84 + 0.49))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.85 / tmp + 0.19)) / 0.32)
    v0 = ((0.27 * v2) - ((v0 + 0.60 / v1 + 0.22) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.69)))
    data[tid] = v0
